1. How to run test drivers: Download the zip file and put it in the package
explorer. Then open up the test folder and default package, and double click
on the SelectionSortTest.java file. Simply run this, and it should check all
of the test cases.

2. The run time of my test case with 1000 array entries was 0.004 seconds 
according to the eclipse JUnit test case compiler. This makes sense because
the c in front of the n^2 run time is likely very small.